<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<android.support.constraint.ConstraintLayout
    xmlns:android="http://schemas.android.com/apk/res/android" android:layout_width="match_parent"
    android:layout_height="match_parent">
    <ScrollView
        android:id="@+id/ScrollViewTipsLayout"
        android:layout_width="fill_parent"
        android:layout_height="fill_parent"
        xmlns:android="http://schemas.android.com/apk/res/android">
        <RelativeLayout xmlns:android="http://schemas.android.com/apk/res/android"
            xmlns:tools="http://schemas.android.com/tools"
            android:layout_width="match_parent"
            android:layout_height="match_parent"
            tools:layout_editor_absoluteX="0dp"
            tools:layout_editor_absoluteY="0dp">


            <RelativeLayout xmlns:android="http://schemas.android.com/apk/res/android"
                xmlns:tools="http://schemas.android.com/tools"
                android:layout_width="match_parent"
                android:layout_height="match_parent"
                android:background="#d5d5d5"
         >

                <ImageView
                    android:id="@+id/img_championbig_actcounters"
                    android:layout_width="wrap_content"
                    android:layout_height="wrap_content"
                    android:layout_alignBottom="@+id/RelativeLayout"
                    android:layout_alignParentEnd="true"
                    android:layout_alignParentLeft="true"
                    android:layout_alignParentRight="true"
                    android:layout_alignParentStart="true"
                    android:layout_alignParentTop="true"
                    android:alpha="0"
                    android:scaleType="centerCrop" />

                <RelativeLayout
                    android:id="@+id/RelativeLayout"
                    android:layout_width="match_parent"
                    android:layout_height="150dp"
                    android:background="#64232323"
                    android:layout_alignParentTop="true"
                    android:layout_alignParentLeft="true"
                    android:layout_alignParentStart="true">

                </RelativeLayout>

                <RelativeLayout
                    android:id="@+id/RelativeLayout2"
                    android:layout_width="wrap_content"
                    android:layout_height="wrap_content"
                    android:layout_alignParentLeft="true"
                    android:layout_alignParentStart="true"
                    android:layout_alignParentTop="true"
                    android:layout_marginLeft="10dp"
                    android:layout_marginTop="30dp"
                    android:background="#e6232323">

                    <ImageView
                        android:id="@+id/imageView2"
                        android:layout_width="100dp"
                        android:layout_height="180dp"
                        android:layout_alignEnd="@+id/img_champion_actcounters"
                        android:layout_alignRight="@+id/img_champion_actcounters"
                        android:layout_marginLeft="2.5dp"
                        android:layout_marginTop="2.5dp"
                        android:background="#232323"
                        android:src="@drawable/hecarim_0" />

                    <ImageView
                        android:id="@+id/img_champion_actcounters"
                        android:layout_width="100dp"
                        android:layout_height="180dp"
                        android:layout_alignParentLeft="true"

                        android:layout_alignParentStart="true"
                        android:layout_alignParentTop="true"
                        android:layout_marginLeft="2.5dp"
                        android:layout_marginTop="2.5dp"
                        android:adjustViewBounds="true"
                        android:alpha="0"
                        android:background="#232323" />


                </RelativeLayout>

                <LinearLayout
                    android:id="@+id/LinearLayout"
                    android:layout_width="wrap_content"
                    android:layout_height="wrap_content"
                    android:layout_marginLeft="125dp"
                    android:layout_marginStart="125dp"
                    android:layout_marginTop="88dp"
                    android:background="#e6232323"
                    android:orientation="vertical"
                    android:paddingBottom="3dp"
                    android:paddingEnd="6dp"
                    android:paddingStart="6dp"
                    android:paddingTop="3dp">

                    <TextView
                        android:id="@+id/tv_champion_name_actcounters"

                        android:layout_width="wrap_content"
                        android:layout_height="wrap_content"
                        android:layout_marginTop="-6dp"
                        android:text="Hecarim"
                        android:textAllCaps="false"
                        android:textColor="#cccc00"
                        android:textSize="18dp"
                        android:textStyle="bold" />

                    <TextView
                        android:id="@+id/tv_champion_title_actcounters"
                        android:layout_width="wrap_content"
                        android:layout_height="wrap_content"
                        android:layout_marginTop="-5dp"
                        android:lineSpacingExtra="-5dp"
                        android:singleLine="false"
android:text="The Shadow of War"
                        android:textColor="#b7b7b7"
                        android:textIsSelectable="false"
                        android:textSize="14dp"
                        android:textStyle="italic" />

                    <LinearLayout
                        android:layout_width="wrap_content"
                        android:layout_height="wrap_content"
                        android:layout_marginTop="-2dp"
                        android:orientation="horizontal">

                        <TextView
                            android:id="@+id/tv_champion_primaryrole_actcounters"
                            android:layout_width="wrap_content"
                            android:layout_height="wrap_content"
                            android:layout_weight="1"
                            android:singleLine="false"
                            android:text="Tank/"
                            android:textColor="#F0F8FF"
                            android:textIsSelectable="false"
                            android:textSize="10dp"
                            android:textStyle="italic" />

                        <TextView
                            android:id="@+id/tv_champion_secondaryrole_actcounters"
                            android:layout_width="wrap_content"
                            android:layout_height="wrap_content"
                            android:layout_weight="1"
                            android:singleLine="false"
                            android:text="Fighter"
                            android:textColor="#b7b7b7"
                            android:textIsSelectable="false"
                            android:textSize="10dp"
                            android:textStyle="italic" />
                    </LinearLayout>

                </LinearLayout>

                <LinearLayout
                    android:id="@+id/LinearLayout2"
                    android:layout_width="match_parent"
                    android:layout_height="wrap_content"
                    android:layout_alignBottom="@+id/RelativeLayout2"
                    android:layout_below="@+id/img_championbig_actcounters"
                    android:layout_marginBottom="15dp"
                    android:layout_toEndOf="@+id/RelativeLayout2"
                    android:layout_toRightOf="@+id/RelativeLayout2"
                    android:orientation="horizontal">

                    <Button
                        android:id="@+id/btn_champion_role_jungle_actcounters"
                        android:layout_width="wrap_content"
                        android:layout_height="35dp"
                        android:layout_marginLeft="1dp"
                        android:layout_marginRight="1dp"
                        android:layout_marginTop="5dp"
                        android:layout_weight="1"
                        android:background="#232323"
                        android:text="@string/btn_champion_role_jungle_actcounters"
                        android:textColor="#006e9e"
                        android:textSize="10dp"
                        android:onClick="Jungle"/>

                    <Button
                        android:id="@+id/btn_champion_role_top_actcounters"
                        android:layout_width="wrap_content"
                        android:layout_height="35dp"
                        android:layout_marginLeft="1dp"
                        android:layout_marginRight="2dp"
                        android:layout_marginTop="5dp"
                        android:layout_weight="1"
                        android:background="#232323"
                        android:text="@string/btn_champion_role_top_actcounters"
                        android:textColor="#006e9e"
                        android:textSize="10dp"
                        android:onClick="Top"/>


                </LinearLayout>


                <RadioGroup
                    android:id="@+id/rg_strong_weak_actcounters"
                    android:layout_width="wrap_content"
                    android:layout_height="wrap_content"
                    android:layout_alignParentEnd="true"
                    android:layout_alignParentRight="true"
                    android:layout_below="@+id/LinearLayout2"
                    android:layout_marginRight="10dp"
                    android:layout_marginTop="-10dp"
                    android:orientation="horizontal">

                    <RadioButton
                        android:id="@+id/rb_strong_against_actcounters"
                        android:layout_width="wrap_content"
                        android:layout_height="wrap_content"
                        android:checked="false"
                        android:text="@string/rb_strong_against_actcounters"
                        android:textSize="14dp" />

                    <RadioButton
                        android:id="@+id/rb_weak_against_actcounters"
                        android:layout_width="wrap_content"
                        android:layout_height="wrap_content"
                        android:checked="false"
                        android:text="@string/rb_weak_against_actcounters"
                        android:textSize="14dp" />
                </RadioGroup>

                <LinearLayout
                    android:layout_width="match_parent"
                    android:layout_height="match_parent"
                    android:orientation="vertical"
                    android:layout_below="@+id/btnSubmit"
                    android:layout_alignParentRight="true"
                    android:layout_alignParentEnd="true">

                    <TextView android:id="@+id/tvIngress5"
                        android:layout_height="wrap_content"
                        android:layout_width="wrap_content"
                        android:text="Passive - Hecarim gains 15% - 30% (based on level) of his bonus movement speed as bonus attack damage."
                        android:layout_span="2"
                        android:singleLine="false"
                        android:layout_weight="1"
                        android:textColor="@color/colorPrimary"
                        android:textSize="5pt"

                        />

                    <TextView android:id="@+id/tvIngress"
                        android:layout_height="wrap_content"
                        android:layout_width="wrap_content"
                        android:text="Q -  Hecarim cleaves nearby enemies, dealing physical damage, reduced to 66.7% against minions."
                        android:layout_span="2"
                        android:singleLine="false"
                        android:layout_weight="1"
                        android:textColor="@color/colorPrimary"
                        android:textSize="5pt"

                        />
                    <TextView android:id="@+id/tvIngres2"
                        android:layout_height="wrap_content"
                        android:layout_width="wrap_content"
                        android:text="W - Hecarim surrounds himself with the spirit of dread for 4 seconds, dealing magic damage per second to all enemies within its reach."
                        android:layout_span="1"
                        android:singleLine="false"
                        android:layout_weight="1"
                        android:textColor="@color/colorPrimary"
                        android:textSize="5pt"
                        />
                    <TextView android:id="@+id/tvIngres3"
                        android:layout_height="wrap_content"
                        android:layout_width="wrap_content"
                        android:text="E - Hecarim is temporarily ghosted and gains bonus movement speed for 4 seconds, beginning at 25% and increasing to 75% over 3 seconds.
While Hecarim is charging, his next basic attack has 325 range, Airborne icon knocks back his target 250 / 450 units, and deals physical damage. The damage and knockback distance are increased based on how far Hecarim travelled during Devastating Charge's duration, ending its effects in the process."
                        android:layout_span="1"
                        android:singleLine="false"
                        android:layout_weight="1"
                        android:textColor="@color/colorPrimary"
                        android:textSize="5pt"
                        />
                    <TextView android:id="@+id/tvIngres4"
                        android:layout_height="wrap_content"
                        android:layout_width="wrap_content"
                        android:text="R - Hecarim summons spectral riders and dashes forth with them in a line, becoming immune to crowd control while charging and dealing magic damage to all enemies in their path. Enemies within range of where Hecarim stops also Fear icon flee from him for 0.75 / 1.5 seconds."
                        android:layout_span="1"
                        android:singleLine="false"
                        android:layout_weight="1"
                        android:textColor="@color/colorPrimary"
                        android:textSize="5pt"
                        />
                    <TextView android:id="@+id/tvIngres6"
                        android:layout_height="wrap_content"
                        android:layout_width="wrap_content"
                        android:text="
   Lore -		Hecarim is an armored colossus who charges from the Shadow Isles at the head of a deathly host of spectral horsemen to hunt the living. A monstrous fusion of man and beast, cursed to ride for eternity, Hecarim revels in slaughter and crushing souls beneath his armored hooves.
Born into an empire long since gone to dust and forgotten, Hecarim was squired to a legendary company of knights known as the Iron Order, a brotherhood sworn to defend their kingâ€™s land. There he endured the harshest training imaginable, a punishing regime that schooled him to be a formidable warrior."
                        android:layout_span="1"
                        android:singleLine="false"
                        android:layout_weight="1"
                        android:textColor="@color/colorPrimary"
                        android:textSize="5pt"
                        />


                </LinearLayout>
                <Spinner
                    android:id="@+id/spinner"
                    android:layout_width="match_parent"
                    android:layout_height="match_parent"
                    android:entries="@string-array/spinItem"
                    android:layout_below="@+id/rg_strong_weak_actcounters"
                    android:layout_alignParentLeft="true"
                    android:layout_alignParentStart="true"
                    android:hint="Favorite Item"
                    android:textColorHint="@color/Gray">

                </Spinner>

                <Button
                    android:id="@+id/btnSubmit"
                    android:layout_width="match_parent"
                    android:layout_height="wrap_content"
                    android:layout_weight="1"
                    android:text="Submit"
                    android:background="@color/DarkGray"
                    android:layout_below="@+id/spinner"
                    android:layout_toRightOf="@+id/LinearLayout"
                    android:layout_toEndOf="@+id/LinearLayout" />
            </RelativeLayout>

        </RelativeLayout>
    </ScrollView>
</android.support.constraint.ConstraintLayout>